OL,3,CHired spotter jailed over gang
OL,4,Cshooting of nine-year-old girl
OL,6,FA hired spotter and getaway driver has
OL,7,Fbeen jailed for life with a minimum
OL,8,Fterm of 34 years for his role in a
OL,9,Fgangland shooting outside a restaurant
OL,10,Fin east London which left a girl of
OL,11,Fnine with a bullet lodged in her brain.
OL,13,FThe girl was hit in the head by one of
OL,14,Fsix bullets fired by a man on a
OL,15,Fpassing motorbike as she sat with her
OL,16,Ffamily in the Evin Restaurant in
OL,17,FKingsland High Street, Hackney, on May
OL,18,F29 last year.
