OL,3,CHired spotter jailed over gang
OL,4,Cshooting of nine-year-old girl
OL,6,FShe was an innocent victim of a bloody
OL,7,Frivalry between Turkish gangs of north
OL,8,FLondon.
OL,10,FThree men at a nearby table were also
OL,11,Finjured.
OL,13,FJavon Riley, 33, from Tottenham, north
OL,14,FLondon, was found guilty at the Old
OL,15,FBailey of causing grievous harm with
OL,16,Fintent to the girl and attempting to
OL,17,Fmurder Mustafa Kiziltan, 35, Kenan
OL,18,FAydogdu, 45, and Nasser Ali, 44.
