OL,3,CHired spotter jailed over gang
OL,4,Cshooting of nine-year-old girl
OL,6,FSentencing him on Friday, Judge Mark
OL,7,FLucraft KC said the gang rivalry had
OL,8,Fseen a number of "tit for tat" murders
OL,9,Fand attempted murders in London and
OL,10,Foverseas over the past 10 years.
OL,12,FThe three men who were shot were said
OL,13,Fto be affiliated with the Hackney
OL,14,FTurks organised crime gang, who had a
OL,15,Frivalry with the Tottenham Turks, with
OL,16,Fwhom Riley had links, jurors had heard.
OL,18,FThe gunman is at large but prosecutors
OL,19,Fsaid Riley had played a "key role"
OL,20,Fbefore, during and after the shooting.
