OL,3,CHired spotter jailed over gang
OL,4,Cshooting of nine-year-old girl
OL,6,FRiley carried out reconnaissance of
OL,7,Fthe restaurant before the attack,
OL,8,Fscouted for potential targets and
OL,9,Fdrove the gunman away in a stolen car,
OL,10,Fwhich was later burnt out.
OL,12,FThe nine-year-old girl spent three
OL,13,Fmonths in hospital and will suffer
OL,14,Fwith lifelong physical and cognitive
OL,15,Fproblems as the bullet remains lodged
OL,16,Fin her brain.
OL,18,FThe three male victims received
OL,19,Fgunshot wounds to the arm, leg and
OL,20,Fthigh.
