OL,4,Cshooting of nine-year-old girl
OL,6,FScotland Yard has offered up to
OL,7,F#15,000 for information leading to the
OL,8,Fidentification, arrest and prosecution
OL,9,Fof the person who fired the shots.
OL,11,FDuring a three-week trial, Riley was
OL,12,Fasked to identify the "third party"
OL,13,Fwho had recruited him for around
OL,14,F#40,000.
OL,16,FHe refused, citing fear for his life
OL,17,Fand that of his family.
