OL,3,CHired spotter jailed over gang
OL,4,Cshooting of nine-year-old girl
OL,6,FThe defendant admitted conducting
OL,7,Freconnaissance, spotting targets and
OL,8,Fpicking up the gunman, but claimed he
OL,9,Fbelieved it was a "smash-and-grab"
OL,10,Frobbery.
OL,12,FHe later admitted the person who used
OL,13,Fthe gun had said to him: "Shots have
OL,14,Fbeen fired. I need to get out of here."
OL,16,FThe court heard Jamaica-born Riley had
OL,17,Fa string of convictions dating back to
OL,18,F2008 including for possession of
OL,19,Fcannabis and cocaine, driving offences
OL,20,Fand having an offensive weapon and a
OL,21,Fblade in his car.
