OL,6,FHe also admitted involvement in car
OL,7,Ftheft, drug dealing and robberies, but
OL,8,Fsaid he had never been caught for
OL,9,Fthose offences.
OL,11,FPolice recordings revealed Riley's
OL,12,Flinks to the Tottenham Turks,
OL,13,Fincluding talks about Izzet Eren, who
OL,14,Fwas shot in Moldova on July 10 last
OL,15,Fyear in what was believed to be a
OL,16,Frevenge attack.
